"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-07-31-olympics-2024-there-will-be-sanctions-sports-min-vows-after-ofilis-100m-race-ban\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Nigeria's sports minister, John Enoh has said he would not tolerate 'utter recklessness' after Nigerian sprinter, Favour Ofili, was denied a 100m race at the ongoing 2024 Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999422666737536, \"rank\": 5.773665542173888e-05, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Enoh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Owan_Enoh\"}, {\"begin\": 114, \"end\": 122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.8060362683224138, \"rank\": 0.24062271805045032, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}, {\"begin\": 133, \"end\": 145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Favour_Ofili\", \"score\": 0.9999688897388217, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Favour Ofili\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Favour_Ofili\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Favour_Ofili\"}, {\"begin\": 202, \"end\": 207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997563991497, \"rank\": 2.4360086650735056e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ofili, in a series of tweets on Tuesday, disclosed she will not take part in the 100m race at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She explained that the reason was because of administrative failures by the Athletics Federation of Nigeria, AFN, and the Nigerian Olympic Committee, NOC.\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9980572844656967, \"rank\": 0.0019464964976489195, \"text\": \"AFN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 441, \"end\": 467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigerian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999921899525667, \"rank\": 7.7873779884345e-06, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, upon hearing Ofili's distress on Tuesday, Enoh said he had reached out to the AFN and the NOC to find out the root cause of the matter.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 562, \"end\": 565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9980572844656967, \"rank\": 0.0019464964976489195, \"text\": \"AFN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\"}, {\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999921899525667, \"rank\": 7.7873779884345e-06, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to him, there will be thorough sanctions after investigations into where and from whom this gross negligence originated.'\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enoh made this known in a statement he personally signed on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, \\\"I reached out to the Athletic Federation of Nigeria (AFN).\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9980572844656967, \"rank\": 0.0019464964976489195, \"text\": \"AFN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Assembly_of_First_Nations\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am in touch with the President of the NOC on this and await his explanation.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 973, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 935, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999921899525667, \"rank\": 7.7873779884345e-06, \"text\": \"NOC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As Minister of Sports, I will not tolerate this utter recklessness.\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is highly inexcusable, and there will be thorough sanctions after investigations into where and from whom this gross negligence originated.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All parties must take their duties very seriously.\\\"\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"US embassy changes service providers in Nigeria over racketeering  Onyeka Onwenu: Her works was timeless - Atiku mourns Singer  Olympics 2024: I borrowed bicycle from Germans to compete - Nigerian cyclist, Ukpeseraye  Paris 2024 Olympics: Ofili reflects on disappointing outing in women's 200m final  Paris 2024 Olympics: Ofili, Oborodudu fail  Paris 2024 Olympics: Ofili reaches women's 200m final  Paris 2024 Olympics: Ofili reflects on women's 200m semi-final feat  Olympics 2024: 'Great rivalry has been created' - Lacazette on France beating Argentina  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1242, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9941918245372323, \"rank\": 0.0029817812950206457, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1282, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9999422666737536, \"rank\": 5.773665542173888e-05, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1309, \"end\": 1322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Onyeka_Onwenu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Onyeka Onwenu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Onyeka_Onwenu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Onyeka_Onwenu\"}, {\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.956014363244, \"rank\": 0.045083523780824586, \"text\": \"Germans\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany